overview:
Pat Washburn is the Editor at OrganizedWisdom Health. She is responsible for helping ensure the safety and quality standards set by the physician review board get implemented on every WisdomCard. She is an experienced editor and longtime healthcare blogger. Previously, Pat was an editor at Eons.com, producing content for an over-50 audience in areas including health, relationships and life goals. At Boston.com, she served as a news producer, and as executive producer of OurMaine.com, she earned two Edward R. Murrow Awards for Best Web Site.

via: OrganizedWisdom
